videoproto
------------------------------------------
X.org VideoProto protocol headers

Runtime requirements:
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  xorg-util-macros-1.20.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.x.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.x.org/releases/individual/proto/videoproto-2.3.3.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack videoproto-2.3.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./videoproto-2.3.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/videoproto-2.3.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/videoproto-2.3.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(videoproto)
  /usr/include/X11/extensions/Xv.h
  /usr/include/X11/extensions/XvMC.h
  /usr/include/X11/extensions/XvMCproto.h
  /usr/include/X11/extensions/Xvproto.h
  /usr/include/X11/extensions/vldXvMC.h
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/videoproto.pc
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/videoproto.README
  /usr/share/doc/videoproto/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/videoproto/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/videoproto/README
  /usr/share/doc/videoproto/xv-protocol-v2.txt

